neoclassical and turbulent theoretical predictions. An analysis with the 1D 
impurity transport code ITC shows the existence of a central zone with reduced 
diffusion and indication of an inward convection. These results are completed 
with theoretical simulations of neoclassical transport (NCLASS) and turbulent 
