coordinate perturbation method to the Poincare-Cartan-Einstein 1-form. General 
gyrokinetic Vlasov-Maxwell equations are then developed as the Vlasov-Maxwell 
equations in the gyrocenter coordinate system, rather than a set of new 
equations. Because the general gyrokinetic system developed is geometrically 
