associated with the coordinate transformation is shown to be an indispensable 
part of the general gyrokinetic Vlasov-Maxwell equations. As an example, the 
pullback transformation in the gyrokinetic Poisson equation is explicitly 
expressed in terms of moments of the gyrocenter distribution function, with the 
important gyro-orbit squeezing effect due to the large electric field shearing 
